OLYMPIC sprint legend Usain Bolt will be track side to inspire athletes when this year’s second PUMA School of Speed takes place at Ruimsig Stadium on Monday.Bolt is the Principal of the PUMA School of Speed, a national series of 5 track meets for high school teens hosted by PUMA and Stillwater Sports, together with sponsor Spur Steak Ranches. Endorsed by athletics federations, the meets feature sprint races as well as short hurdles, long jump and high jump, with PUMA contracts among the prizes up for grabs.The sprint legend is set to delight fans and athletes with a parade around the Ruimsig track before the day’s finals are run, handing out PUMA School of Speed memorabilia and posing for photos in his iconic Lightning Bolt pose.if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsuL9OgBBH4WAolrh6_VXpr-MXmHYZ1NiFuj--PAC1dWhCs_K4O_9WMtxrPTEx6JZPi0vepTmn-WZzt7I0kWXd8Q4tN5gD-fCc6M88KM5tm5U7YJZy1X4Wo8-OGJm2SlMQu4oMQ9J0jIEkmc-iMf360R-USD957lnJsoBcByLhhou1QiIBR_7z6t2mcCqhON9cZjCGy-T1pmdNlTfbkTRGGGl2xrHVYKxUzzGxvUDTYyjW8xN8Nf2xrdHvigclkqWFkop1FYEpBWxCAw5PWB\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzG9U5fcwnpn6EAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
